    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the potatoes have had an initial 20 min, remove the tray from the oven and add the<strong> stuffing-topped pork loin steaks</strong> to the tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>to the oven for a final 13-15 min or until the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> roast pork loin with fennel stuffing</strong></p>",
